WITH del_leases AS (
            DELETE FROM leases
            WHERE message_id = $1
        ),
        ins_failed AS (
            INSERT INTO attempts_failed (
                id,
                message_id,
                failed_at,
                attempted,
                retry_earliest_at
            )
            VALUES ($2, $1, $3, $4, $5)
        )
        INSERT INTO errors (
            id,
            message_id,
            reported_at,
            error
        )
        VALUES ($6, $1, $3, $7)
